N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 143.12 - Other laws and regulations; interstate movement of regulated articles

State Regulations

This Part shall only apply to the intrastate movement of
regulated articles. No provision of this Part relieves any person from the
obligation to comply with any additional applicable federal, state, county, regional or local law or regulation. Notes
